      <hedline>
        <hl1>NBC Will Begin Olympics Promotion</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By BERNARD STAMLER</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Stamler, Bernard</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>NBC, using campaign created in-house, to begin promotional campaign for Summer Olympics in Sydney, Australia, that network will broadcast (Advertising column) (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>It may be months before the Summer Olympics in Sydney, Australia, but the network that will broadcast the games, NBC, is starting a promotional campaign.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>It may be months before the Summer Olympics in Sydney, Australia, but the network that will broadcast the games, NBC, is starting a promotional campaign.</p>
        <p>The campaign, created in-house, starts tonight with a commercial during the season finale of ''E.R.'' It features the American athletes C. J. Hunter and Marion Jones. NBC, part of the General Electric Company, also plans a spot with the sprinter Michael Johnson and commercials with cast members of the comedies ''Frasier'' and ''Will and Grace.''</p>
        <p>THE MEDIA BUSINESS: ADVERTISING -- ADDENDA</p>
      </block>
